"Balgruuf: Well done. You sought me out, on your own initiative. You've done          Whiterun a service, and I won't forget it. Here, take this as a small          token of my esteem. There is another thing you could do for me.          Suitable for someone of your particular talents, perhaps. Come, let's          go find Farengar, my court wizard. He's been looking into a matter          related to these dragons and...rumors of dragons.",
