"You've done a great service to me and my city, Dragonborn. By my          right as Jarl, I name you Thane of Whiterun. It's the greatest honor          that's within my power to grant. I assign you Lydia as a personal          housecarl, and this weapon from my armory to serve as your badge of          office. I'll also notify my guards of your new title. Wouldn't want          them to think you're part of the common rabble, now would we? We are          honored to have you as Thane of our city, Dragonborn.",
"Back to business, Proventus. We still have a city to defend.",
