"Tolfdir: I'm sure you've already noticed the markings. They're quite unlike         anything we've seen before. Ayleid, Dwemer, Daedric... Not even         Falmer. None of them are a match. Quite curious indeed. Now, I'm not         sure you're quite as attuned as I am, given my extensive years of         experience, but can you feel that? This marvelous object. It         practically radiates magicka, and yet it's unlike anything I've felt         before. Arch-Mage Aren is already hard at work, and hopefully we'll         have more information soon.",
"Ancano: I'm afraid I must intrude. It is urgent that I speak with your        associate immediately.",
