"Why side with the Empire?          ¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯           Mutual advantage! Any fool can see that. For centuries, we have           benefited from the Empire's protection, and prosperous trade with           the south. In exchange, the people of Cyrodiil sleep peacefully,           knowing their northern borders are guarded by the fiercest warriors           in all Tamriel.",
