"This is no ruse. I want to keep her safe.²          ¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯           Coming from one who murders vampires as a trade, I find it hard to           believe your intentions are noble.",
