"Perhaps her death is destined.          ¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯           No! I will not allow that to happen. The Elder Scrolls only tell of           events that might be, not events that will be.",
"Dragonborn: And Serana's opinion on this?",
"Valerica: You care nothing for Serana or our plight.           • You see the Tyranny of the Sun as your chance at deification, and            like Harkon you won't hesitate to destroy anything that stands in            your path.",
