"We could use your help in Tamriel.           ¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯            As much as it pains me to send you and Serana back alone, I can't            take the risk.",
