"Serana: I'm glad we found the scroll, but I...I wish she could come with us.",
"Dragonborn: Why don't you come back with us?",
"Valerica: Even if I could, it would only serve to hinder your efforts. Harkon          would likely sense my return to Tamriel. The last thing you need          right now is a trail for him to follow.",
